metadata.name: The Serenade for Frida
metadata.description:
This cubist style art piece was inspired by the love story of Diego Rivera and Frida Kahlo, and depicts a moonlight serenade by Diego where he brings Frida a bouquet of calla lilies and a declaration of love. 

I created this original oil painting on canvas;
Height: 40" inches
Length: 30" inches
Width: 7/8" inches
